# CLIP Changelog for sys-apps/pcsc-lite

*pcsc-lite-1.8.9 (18 Oct 2016)

  18 Oct 2016; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r7.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r6.ebuild:
  Added dependency on jail_init virtual service provided by init_cgroups.

*pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r6 (25 Mar 2015)

  25 Mar 2015; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r6.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r5.ebuild,
  files/jails/pcsc/fstab.internal:
  Set the jail's root read-only.

*pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r5 (26 Feb 2015)

  26 Feb 2015; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r5.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r4.ebuild:
  Create additional export directory in pcsc vserver needed
  by smartcard-monitor.

*pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r4 (05 May 2014)

  05 May 2014; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r4.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r3.ebuild,
  files/jails/pcsc/nscleanup:
  Unmount /home/user as needed when setting up the pcsc jail.

*pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r3 (30 Dec 2013)

  30 Dec 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r3.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r2.ebuild:
  Force rebuild to add openrc dependency.

*pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r2 (14 Nov 2013)

  14 Nov 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r2.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r1.ebuild,
  files/pcscd-init.4.clip:
  Don't run pcsc unless SMARTCARD_SUPPORT=yes is present
  in /etc/admin/conf.d/smartcards.

*pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r1 (14 Nov 2013)

  14 Nov 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.8-r1.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.8.ebuild,
  files/pcscd-init.4.clip:
