*pcsc-lite-1.8.6-r1 (19 Oct 2012)

  19 Oct 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pcsc-lite-1.8.6-r1.ebuild, -pcsc-lite-1.8.6.ebuild,
  files/jails/pcsc/fstab.external:
  Add 'nodev' to /sys mount options in the pcsc jail, otherwise
  devctl will reject this mount.

*pcsc-lite-1.8.6 (04 Oct 2012)

  04 Oct 2012; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
